<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    .logo {
      background-image: radial-gradient(#eb568e, #144ee3);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer-header {
      margin: 1.5rem;
    }
    .bg {
      width: 100%; /* Adjust image width as needed */
      height: auto;
      display: block; /* Ensure the image is a block-level element */
      margin-top: 2rem; /* Add spacing between image and content */
    }
    footer {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      border-top: 0.5rem solid blue;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    ul {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      list-style-type: none;
    }
    li {
      font-size: 13px;
      margin: 8px;
    }
    .left {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .sign {
      width: 30%;
    }
  </style>
  <title>Linkly</title>
</head>
<body style="background-color: #0e131e" class="text-light mx-5">
  <nav class="navbar navbar-light" style="background-color: #0e131e;">
    <h1 class="logo">Linkly</h1>
    <div>
      <a href="/login">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Login</button>
      </a>
      <a href="/signup">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary">Register</button>
      </a>
    </div>
  </nav>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col left">
        <h1 class="text-light">More than just <br> shorter links</h1>
        <p class="text-light">Shorten your links easily and get insights on how your links are performing.</p>
        <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-primary sign">Get started</a>
      </div>
      <div class="col">
        <img src="/illustration-working.svg" alt="User image" class="bg">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h1>Simple and fast URL shortener!</h1>
      <p>ShortURL allows you to shorten long links from various platforms and track their performance.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h1>Shorten, share, and track</h1>
      <p>Your shortened URLs can be used in various locations and tracked for business insights.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <footer>
    <h4 class="footer-header">&copy; 2024 Linkly.at - Tool to shorten a long link</h4>
    <div>
      <ul class="list">
        <li>ShortUrl</li>
        <li>URL click Counter</li>
        <li>Unshorten Url</li>
        <li>Terms of service</li>
        <li>Privacy</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
